:"是啊，毕竟机会难得，"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":100}],"textRight":"我想要做出能够成为游乐园卖点的@招牌菜单。"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":7007,"name":"sprite_0"}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":6007,"name":"sprite_0","pos":0}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"[chara:6007:effect_emotion_sad_0][se:7224_fall_into]我不是很懂人类的食物咕噜。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":300}],"textRight":"也对哦，"},{"chara":[{"id":110300}],"textRight":"那只能我自己来想了。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":201}],"textRight":"我要想出一个@足以超越全盛时期万万岁的特别菜单！"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"id":7007,"name":"sprite_0","pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":110300,"motion":300}],"textRight":"虽然我干劲十足地这么说了……@但总觉得不对头。","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":7007,"name":"sprite_0"}],"nameLeft":"","textLeft":"是吗啪咔？"},{"chara":[{"id":110300}],"textRight":"嗯……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":0}],"textRight":"如果是尽全力做出来的超厉害菜品，@那吃饭的人也会觉得紧张的。"},{"chara":[{"id":7007,"name":"sprite_0"}],"textLeft":"是这样啊啪咔？"},{"chara":[{"id":110300}],"textRight":"嗯。"},{"chara":[{"id":110300,"motion":100}],"textRight":"我在万万岁的时候@有些努力过头了。"},{"chara":[{"id":110300}],"textRight":"我不想做这样的菜……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":1}],"textRight":"我想做更加悠闲、@能让人放松的菜品……"},{"nameNarration":"鹤乃","narration":"跟合得来的朋友在喜欢的地方……","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"热热闹闹、开开心心地……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","textRight":"[chara:110300:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]啊……"},{"chara":[{"id":7007,"name":"sprite_0"},{"id":110300,"mouthOpen":0}],"textLeft":"想出些什么了吗啪咔？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":110300,"motion":0}],"textRight":"嗯！"},{"ch